Tupinamba-0011_03,Tupinamba,Opa ko mo mosapɨr mɨsã ʔara sɨkeme , apɨaβamo osɨ rɨge swi Tupã taʔɨra ʔarʔire , mosapɨr moruβiʃaβa , Reis ʔiaβa , kwarasɨ semaβa kotɨ swi ourɨβaʔe , jasɨtata serekoarama rese , Tupã remimojanga pɨsasu pe jaramo iʃupe ogueru jetanongaβamo itajuβa , ɨsɨkatã sɨapwanɨβaʔe , mirra , mosanga toʔo swi",,,"Three chiefs, said to be king, who came from the orient through the guardian star that god had made new as indicator of the path, brought him as offering: gold, incense and myhrr, after god's son was born from his mother's womb, when the thirteenth day came  Catalogo January 6",English,,"# sent_id = 0011.03

# text = Opa ko mo mosapɨr mɨsã ʔara sɨkeme , apɨaβamo osɨ rɨge swi Tupã taʔɨra ʔarʔire , mosapɨr moruβiʃaβa , Reis ʔiaβa , kwarasɨ semaβa kotɨ swi ourɨβaʔe , jasɨtata serekoarama rese , Tupã remimojanga pɨsasu pe jaramo iʃupe ogueru jetanongaβamo itajuβa , ɨsɨkatã sɨapwanɨβaʔe , mirra , mosanga toʔo swi

# text_eng = Three chiefs, said to be king, who came from the orient through the guardian star that god had made new as indicator of the path, brought him as offering: gold, incense and myhrr, after god's son was born from his mother's womb, when the thirteenth day came  Catalogo January 6

,UD_Tupinamba-TuDeT
